Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:46.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU] Yes. Ginko committed\Na grave crime, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:49.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko is the reason\Nwhy Sumika is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:56.85,Main,,0,0,0,,How could you, Ginko?\NI'll never forgive you bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:01:00.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin you, now. Every one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:04.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[gunshot]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:08.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NGrowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:19.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] From the beginning,\Nwe hated you. But also,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:23.04,Main,,0,0,0,,we loved you from the\Nbeginning, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:26.29,Main,,0,0,0,,All we wanted was to become\Ntrue friends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:31.17,Main,,0,0,0,,So we had to cross the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:36.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO, LULU]\NYurikuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:12.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS chat]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NGirls, this is, like, way bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.61,Main,,0,0,0,,People are saying another\Nbear was here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:19.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT A] Yeah, but I heard\Nit was exterminated immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENT B]\NThat same girl shot it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,The one The Invisible Storm\Nisn't a huge fan of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:27.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but, and don't tell anyone\Ncuz it's, like, way secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:30.96,Main,,0,0,0,,apparently that bear is,\Nlike, way still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the\NDoor to Friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:13.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko, you silly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] I've finally\Ngotten rid of the nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:32.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro, you are the\Ngirl Reia gave her pendant to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:35.19,Main,,0,0,0,,on that stormy\Nnight so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:38.94,Main,,0,0,0,,And what a stupid girl you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:42.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Instead of getting love,\Nyou fell into the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:46.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all your own fault, dear.\NYou knew Lulu Yurigasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:49.41,Main,,0,0,0,,loved you, but you\Npretended not to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.62,Main,,0,0,0,,And then you tried\Nto abandon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:55.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, you're paying the\Nprice for that sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess what, Reia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:05:00.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Your sweet girl, the precious\Ndaughter you loved so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.93,Main,,0,0,0,,is almost mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.35,Main,,0,0,0,,And now I'll make her\Nmy bride-in-the-box.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:10.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[BEAR SHOCK LADY]\NShock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuma shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:15.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] I'm going to eat\NKureha Tsubaki! Grrraow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:17.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:23.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] You should be\Nthankful you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.91,Main,,0,0,0,,For now, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:35.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodness, did I surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:38.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you here? I thought\Nyou were dead. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:41.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you thought right,\Nbecause I am dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's crazy, but you're the only\None who can see me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:49.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything's fine.\NJust think of me as a ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:52.81,Main,,0,0,0,,named "Desire" that happens\Nto dwell inside you right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:53.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[laughs] Is that\Nexplanation enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NWhere are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NThe Door to Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.78,Main,,0,0,0,,The center of the\Nsky that divides
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.95,Main,,0,0,0,,the worlds of moon and forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:09.04,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the place where\Ntrue love is tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, tell me\Nsomething, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm dying to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:15.17,Main,,0,0,0,,how you were the one who\Nkilled Sumika Izumino.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:20.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] I say early tomorrow\Nmorning we come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, the flowerbed\Ncan get fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't mind helping\Nyou at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:27.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mitsuko, that's\Nso generous of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Great. We're both in, are\Nyou meeting us too, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:35.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA, KUREHA gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:36.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:42.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] I sensed\Nsomething was wrong, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I had a rival at the\Nschool who was also
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.07,Main,,0,0,0,,after my Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:53.29,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear in human form other\Nthan me. Well me and Konomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:55.12,Main,,0,0,0,,If I didn't hurry\Nand make my move,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:58.92,Main,,0,0,0,,another bear was going to get\Nto her before I could. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Bye. I'm headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.05,Main,,0,0,0,,See you in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Listen, Sumika.\NI have an idea about tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't we arrange\Na surprise for Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NA surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I know someone with lilies\Nin bloom who would probably
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,give us some. Don't you\Nthink she'd love that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.61,0:07:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I can pick them up tonight so\Nwe can plant them for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It'll be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:29.49,Main,,0,0,0,,So, tomorrow morning meet me\Nthere early, and together we'll
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.66,Main,,0,0,0,,fill the flowerbed full of\Nlilies before she arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, but what if she--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:37.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet it will make\NKureha so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be just like a\Nmagic fairy visited!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NUh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,It's funny. That girl\Nwould've done anything I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:51.39,Main,,0,0,0,,All I had to do was\Nmention it was for Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:55.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, come on, be honest\Nwith me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.48,Main,,0,0,0,,--[crunch]\N--[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:01.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NThe truth is, you found out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:05.07,Main,,0,0,0,,that I was targeting\NSumika Izumino, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] You should learn\Nhow to hide better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew all along you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:18.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Following Sumika to see\Nwhat made her so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you get some?\NThey are very lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:27.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] What? Oh, you're one of\Nthe new transfer students, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NSniff, sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.64,Main,,0,0,0,,--[SUMIKA laughs]\N--[GINKO] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,They smell amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:38.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing you must\Nbe a fan of lilies, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I adore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.98,Main,,0,0,0,,They're lovely, and they make\Nme think of a special memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:48.15,Main,,0,0,0,,A special memory with a friend,\Na friend I happen to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA] I won't back\Ndown on that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:55.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Because the love\Nmy friend gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:58.33,Main,,0,0,0,,can't be taken away by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA gasps]\NOh! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:05.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet it was weird for me\Nto say something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,when we've only just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:10.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Yeah. You were\Njealous of her, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:14.30,Main,,0,0,0,,The love you dreamed about,\Nand wanted so badly from Kureha,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:17.56,Main,,0,0,0,,had already been\Ngiven to another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NGrowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:26.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] And yet, you still\Nwanted to see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:29.28,Main,,0,0,0,,In fact, this time you didn't\Neven tell your partner
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.45,Main,,0,0,0,,what you were up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Why go? Did you plan\Nto warn her about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:37.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NYes. That was the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, stupid me. How could I go\Nand lose the hairpin again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:46.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NUh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA]\NGinko! You found it! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.76,Main,,0,0,0,,What a relief!\NI'm so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the second time\Nsomeone's found this pin for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost it the day of the\Nentrance ceremony, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.69,Main,,0,0,0,,The friend I told you\Nabout yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.65,Main,,0,0,0,,She's the one who who found\Nit before. Neat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:09.44,Main,,0,0,0,,She found it\Nfor you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:13.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep. This hairpin has brought\Nme friendship and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I like to think of it\Nas my special charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you,\Nit means so much to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:21.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I really, really\Nappreciate it, Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:24.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, I'd better hurry up\Nand run, or I'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:26.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]\NWai--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:36.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I was first, though. She\Nfound me first. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:41.14,Main,,0,0,0,,If you had gone ahead\Nand stopped her then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika Izumino wouldn't have\Nhad to die. Kureha Tsubaki
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,wouldn't have had to lose\Nher very best friend, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:54.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I know. I couldn't\Nhelp it. Sumika was in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO laughs] And we\Nexclude those in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.45,Main,,0,0,0,,It would be so much easier\Nif we were just honest
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:03.79,Main,,0,0,0,,about what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:10.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] So that's the truth. I'm\Nguilty. I wanted Sumika to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NWell, good morning, Sumika!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[SUMIKA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:19.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\NShock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:21.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Kuma shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Such a lovely morning.\NAnd I'm practically starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl-growl\NChomp-chomp...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You witnessed me attacking\Nsweet little Sumika,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:33.40,Main,,0,0,0,,and you just sat there and\Nwatched. You allowed her die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:37.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You could've saved her,\Nbut you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:39.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Technically, yes,\NI'm the one who ate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:43.79,Main,,0,0,0,,But who was the one\Nthat really killed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:44.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NIndeed it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:49.58,Main,,0,0,0,,In that moment,\Nyou were a slave of desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Jealousy got ahold of you and\Ndrove you to a terrible crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I'm a criminal bear.\NGrowl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:58.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Yes. However,\Nis there really any creature
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,that doesn't sin\Nin order to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki forgot you,\Nher friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:08.19,Main,,0,0,0,,and then she gave her\Nlove to Sumika instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:12.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, pay attention. Only one\Nthing in this world is certain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.86,Main,,0,0,0,,and, believe you me,\Nit's not friendship or love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:20.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Desire is the only thing\Nyou can count on, dear Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:25.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Love is a savage emotion.\NTo love another is to rule them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:27.29,Main,,0,0,0,,To want to become one with them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,so badly you consume\Nthem is truly cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:34.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I know something else you might\Nwant to hear. Shall I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:37.72,Main,,0,0,0,,There's another bear at\Nthat school besides us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,A very cunning bear, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.97,Main,,0,0,0,,She got Kureha to kill me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.76,Main,,0,0,0,,and she got Lulu Yurigasaki\Nto betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it, but that\Nbitch-bear had all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.48,Main,,0,0,0,,dancing to her\Nown little tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NChomp, chomp, grrraow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO] Everything she's done\Nis because she's after Kureha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.94,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry and stop her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,you'll lose Kureha\Nforever this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to become\None with me, Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:11.71,Main,,0,0,0,,The time has come\Nto prove your love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[MITSUKO]\NGraow, graow, graow, graow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:28.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl, ha, ha, ha, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:33.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[FEMALE VOICE]\N♪ Kuma ga aku. ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:42.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO] I'm going to eat her.\NI have to. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:53.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[sirens blaring]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] These photos were\Ntotally discovered in the locker
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,of Kaoru Harishima,\Nwho recently, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.55,Main,,0,0,0,,way died in a bear attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:09.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Konomi Yurikawa,\Nas you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:13.23,Main,,0,0,0,,was actually a bear\Ndisguised as a human girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.94,Main,,0,0,0,,This is scary, like way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:21.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears got across the wall\Npretending to be human,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:25.53,Main,,0,0,0,,and they've like way eaten our\Nfriends one after the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:27.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[STUDENTS murmur]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:32.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] We all see what this,\Nlike, means, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.46,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, there's,\Nlike, a bear in this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.29,Main,,0,0,0,,A bear hiding among us,\Nlike, for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:41.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] Bears, like, way\Nstick out from our crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:43.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears refuse to\Nlike fit in with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:47.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears are evil and can't\Nfollow social cues!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL] Here we go.\NThey've started up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:54.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE BEAUTY]\NYep, but, Kureha Tsubaki
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:56.40,Main,,0,0,0,,is attending the\Nmeeting this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:58.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL] They made her\Na friend at this late date?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:02.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Very interesting. Have they\Ncanceled her exclusion, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:05.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NOh, who can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:09.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Those girls are always looking\Nfor some "evil" to exclude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:10.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter to\Nthem whether the evil
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,is a person or a bear\Nor even really evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:17.46,Main,,0,0,0,,The ritual of banding together\Nto exclude someone is what
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,makes the invisible connection\Nthey like to call "Us"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:22.67,Main,,0,0,0,,feel as if it is real to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:27.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh! It looks like they're\Nalmost there. For that is sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[beep]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL]\NShall I put in another coin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY]\NYeah. Shaba-da... doo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:43.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO] Let us now begin\Nthe Exclusion Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Please name whom we think\Nthe bear lurking among us is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:50.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's search bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:28.15,Main,,0,0,0,,People who, like, shelter\Nbears are accomplices!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:32.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:36.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NTell me, Mom. Did I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:38.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Did I do the right\Nthing that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NLulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:46.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[LULU]\NKure-pie. Lulu knows the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,She found out what\NGinko did to Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Ginko committed a\Nvery grave crime, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko is why Sumika's dead.\NShe helped the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:17:00.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Ginko, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[GINKO]\NYes, it's true. Growl, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:07.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I killed Sumika Izumino.\NIt was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:13.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[music box plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:18.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NMitsuko Yurizono killed Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:24.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I know that for a fact, so,\Nwhy would Ginko confess to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the truth,\Nand what's a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:30.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[MODIFIED VOICE]\NIs your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:46.32,Main,,0,0,0,,This call is a challenge\Nfrom the Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:48.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[MODIFIED VOICE]\N...if your love is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:52.65,Main,,0,0,0,,go to the lily bed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.95,Main,,0,0,0,,The bear in question\Nwill be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]\NShe's at the flowerbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:58.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko's waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:01.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NGive yourself over to the bears,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,and your love will be approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:06.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NI'm going to go talk to Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:10.21,Main,,0,0,0,,And this time, I'm going to\Nfind out what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:12.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE COOL] Huh. To think\Nshe masqueraded as us
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:15.89,Main,,0,0,0,,to make a prank call\Nto Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:19.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that Yuriika Hakonaka.\NShe is guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:22.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE BEAUTY] Mm-hm. Although,\Nwhat she's about to do
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.69,Main,,0,0,0,,is why she made the contract\Nwith us to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:29.40,Main,,0,0,0,,So, she's probably ready for the\Nconsequences. Sparkle, sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:32.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[LIFE SEXY] All shall be as\Naccording to Kumaria's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:37.20,Main,,0,0,0,,For that is sexy. Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Ginko, what\Nhappened between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:46.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:54.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] Dearest Reia, do you\Nremember that stormy night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:57.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the\Nmoment I ate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:59.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you remember when I put\Nyou in the box of myself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,to fill in my gaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:06.19,Main,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't fulfilled,\NI was still so empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:09.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA laughs]\NI figured out why, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:12.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It was because you had given\Nall your love away to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,So I decided to\Nwait, until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I waited until that girl who\Nstole your love from me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:22.24,Main,,0,0,0,,finally grew up.\NAnd I waited as your love,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,gradually and beautifully,\Nblossomed inside of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:29.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I did all this in a blank\Nworld robbed of color.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:33.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I waited, and\Nwaited, and waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:38.05,Main,,0,0,0,,At last, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,The flower has bloomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Today, I will eat your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Today, I will eat\NKureha Tsubaki. Grraow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:54.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA panting]\NGinko! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] Pant, pant, grrraow.\NPant, pant, grrraow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:00.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NGrrraowrrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:08.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] Uh! This... This is\Nwrong. That bear isn't Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] Oh, Reia.\NShe looks just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:17.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Her eyes, her hair.\NShe even has your smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki!\NGive your love to me! Grrraow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You and I are going\Nto become one forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:37.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Take my kiss, now,\NKureha, my darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:39.45,Main,,0,0,0,,This kiss is a special one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It's for my precious\Nbride-in-the-box.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NGrr-rrao-rraow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,That was, like, a way,\Nsuper close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NChouko? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHOUKO]\NThe bear ran away! After it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:58.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[footsteps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA]\NWait, that's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:06.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:11.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NYuriika. Yuriika. Yuriika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:14.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuriika? Yuriika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA sighs]\NReia, you found me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:23.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I missed you so much. Oh,\Nhow I've longed to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,just one more time, and here you\Nare. It's all I've dreamed about
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:30.08,Main,,0,0,0,,since that awful\Nnight I ate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:33.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Reia. I've been holding\Non to something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I need to return to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:37.84,Main,,0,0,0,,In a box, in the middle\Nof my drawers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.17,Main,,0,0,0,,"The Moon Girl and\Nthe Forest Girl",
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:44.93,Main,,0,0,0,,that box has the rest of\Nyour picture book in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:49.52,Main,,0,0,0,,It was the dream of our\Nlove that never materialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:53.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't seem\Nto help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted it so desperately\NI stole it. Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:07.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NYes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:12.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That will be their destiny.\NTheir rightful future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.58,0:22:16.34,Main,,0,0,0,,You know the truth, don't you,\NReia? You know how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:21.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I think you knew before\NI did. And I still do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:25.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] And we'll be\Nfriends forever, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:30.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[REIA]\NYes. Forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.43,0:22:32.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA]\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.12,0:24:19.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[KUREHA] I can't believe\NMiss Yuriika was the bear
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.54,0:24:21.34,Main,,0,0,0,,that killed Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.84,0:24:26.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[YURIIKA] That will be their\Ndestiny. Their rightful future.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.84,0:24:31.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Here it is. The end.\NGinko's and my future?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.10,0:24:34.02,Main,,0,0,0,,It can't be. That's impossible!
